                <p>To N. American Col. 27,025 To Van Diem. Land 281 <lb/>United States 38,495 West Australia 233 <lb/>West Indies 1,938 Port-Philip 3,201 <lb/>Cape of G. Hope 513 South Australia 2,911 <lb/>Sydney 7,811 New Zealand 1,330 <lb/>Total 83,746</p>
